            "text": " ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "style which brings a known 2D series into 3D and it was certainly a great way for HAL to dip their toe into the third dimensional waters. And yet, I do still hope for a 3D sandbox Kirby game one day, but I'll take what I can get today.",
